title: Pushing Past Your Limits w/ Jesse Itzler
itunes:title: Pushing Past Your Limits w/ Jesse Itzler
description:
Episode 188 -  Jesse Itzler is a serial entrepreneur and owner of the Atlanta Hawks. But even though he is as successful as he is he felt that he was stuck in a rut a few years back. So what did he do? He hired the "toughest man in the world" to come live with him for 30 days to completely shake his life up. This interview is about Jesse having a Navy SEAL live with him for 30 days!
